tweet: Man... just saw the same tweet for 3 times today. It's sick!
Aren't you sick of seeing the same things everytime? I bet i saw a lot of tweets like billion times!
Now we get expect it everywhere that we go. All the things that they say. Yeah we already know..
We say where we're coming from. We've already seen the worst that life can bring.
Look out better play it safe you'll never know what hard times will come your way.
Stop your messing around boy. Better think of your future. Better make some good plans boy. Said every one of my teachers.
Don't really care about the things that they say. Don't really care about what happens to me. I just wanna live.

I'm paranoid of all the people I meet. Why are they talking to me?
And why can't anyone see? I just wanna live.
It's getting hectic everywhere that I go. They wont leave me alone. There's things they all wanna know.
I need an alarm system in my house. So I know when people are creeping about. These people are freaking me out these days.
Don't tell me who I should be. And don't try to tell me what's right for me. Don't tell me what I should do.
You're always there to point out my mistakes and shove them in my face.
You think you are special but I know and I know and I know and we know that you're not.
There you go. You never ask why. It's all a big lie whatever you do.
Nothing you say today is gonna bring me down!
So shut up shut up shut up! Don't wanna hear it! Get up, get up, get up! Get out of my way! Step up, step up, step up! You'll never stop me!
It's like i'm the one you love to hate but not today..
It seems like everyday I make mistakes. I just can't get it right.
You always take time to criticize me.
There you go. You're always so right. It's all a big show. It's all about you. You think you know what everyone needs.
cuz they are not  a faker, a fraud as you always seem to me.
Honestly when i have to be away from Twitter, i'm gon miss only Jedward, Ally, Gökçe and smb (wont tell her name) cuz they're gon miss me 2.
She annoys me..
